# TextRenderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Render bridge for world-space text: sole adder of DrawStringInFrameEvent. Returns early until the
ResourceMapSingletonComponent is present. Each frame it emits one draw event per entity that has a
LabelComponent, a resolved WorldTransformComponent, and a font id present in the resource map's font
map (world matrix + sort key, text, font, colour, kerning, line spacing). Labels with no world
transform yet or an unresolved font id are skipped.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read | Resolves font ids to fonts; guard (returns early if absent) |
| LabelComponent | read | Text + font id + style |
| WorldTransformComponent | read | World matrix + render sort key |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DrawStringInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One per drawable label; consumed by Renderer2DSystem this frame |
